# semble index tuning for this MoonBit repo.
#
# semble does not treat .mbt/.mbti as supported source by default, so without
# this file `semble search` returns zero hits for choir's own code and every
# leaf burns a search-and-discard turn before falling back to grep. The `!`
# negations force MoonBit sources into the index (fallback text chunker until a
# MoonBit tree-sitter grammar lands upstream). Verified empirically: a bare
# .mbt tree indexes nothing; with these negations it indexes and ranks.
!*.mbt
!*.mbti

# The include above would otherwise pull in generated and vendored MoonBit too.
# Keep build artifacts and mooncake deps out of the index.
_build/
target/
.mooncakes/
**/.mooncakes/

# Per-leaf worktrees are full repo checkouts; indexing them duplicates every
# symbol N-fold (one copy per live leaf). Index only the canonical root tree.
.choir/worktrees/
.choir/review-worktrees/
